{
  "stem": "22840.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There had to be, because I remember sliding down with-- slides with children and being chastised very much by the adults.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because when you slide down at all, it becomes more icy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if it becomes more icy, then it's-- it's bad for the adults.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Children could care less-- slide on their bottom, right?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was the first time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I had to be in Bratislava before, because my maternal grandparents lived in Bratislava before they came to Novo Mesto.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had a house there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I have been there visiting them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I recall the big house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My grandmother-- maternal grandmother survived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were many members of-- on my mother's side, her brothers and sisters, which left in the '30s, which decided this is not a place for Jews to be, and left in the '30s.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They went to Argentina.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They went to-- to England, to-- to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- they left the country, and they survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Most of them died within the last two years, three years.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they-- they enjoyed a long, lengthy, fruitful life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I still have from my mother's side-- one sister lives now in Jerusalem.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She was in the British army during the Second World War.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Surgery.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Complication after surgery or from neglect.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were rumors after the war, after he died, that he was killed on purpose-- on-- surgically killed, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There-- there is no support for that story-- not that he didn't have enemies.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And obviously lots of the collaborators of Slovakia which were still alive and knew they were documented would like him to see dead.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there's no-- no support for that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The person who-- who was the-- the surgeon was one of the more respected surgeons somebody knew.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so many respected him.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
